{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Today I want to talk to you about"},{"time":2000,"text":"swimming across the North Pole,"},{"time":5000,"text":"across the most northern place in the whole world."},{"time":7000,"text":"And perhaps the best place to start is with my late father."},{"time":11000,"text":"He was a great storyteller."},{"time":13000,"text":"He could tell a story about an event,"},{"time":16000,"text":"and so you felt you were absolutely there at the moment."},{"time":19000,"text":"And one of the stories he told me so often when I was a young boy"},{"time":22000,"text":"was of the first British atomic bomb test."},{"time":26000,"text":"He had been there and watched it go off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"And he said that the explosion was so loud"},{"time":33000,"text":"and the light was so intense,"},{"time":35000,"text":"that he actually had to put his hands in front of his face to protect his eyes."},{"time":39000,"text":"And he said that he could actually see an x-ray"},{"time":42000,"text":"of his fingers,"},{"time":44000,"text":"because the light was so bright."},{"time":47000,"text":"And I know that watching that atomic bomb going off"},{"time":51000,"text":"had a very, very big impact on my late father."},{"time":54000,"text":"Every holiday I had as a young boy"},{"time":57000,"text":"was in a national park."},{"time":59000,"text":"What he was trying to do with me was to inspire me"},{"time":61000,"text":"to protect the world,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and show me just how fragile the world is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67000,"text":"He also told me about the great explorers."},{"time":70000,"text":"He loved history. He would tell me about Captain Scott"},{"time":73000,"text":"walking all the way to the South Pole"},{"time":75000,"text":"and Sir Edmund Hillary climbing up Mount Everest."},{"time":78000,"text":"And so ever since I think I was just six years old,"},{"time":81000,"text":"I dreamed of going to the polar regions."},{"time":83000,"text":"I really, really wanted to go to the Arctic."},{"time":86000,"text":"There was something about that place"},{"time":88000,"text":"which drew me to it."},{"time":90000,"text":"And, well, sometimes it takes a long time"},{"time":93000,"text":"for a dream to come true."},{"time":95000,"text":"But seven years ago, I went to the Arctic"},{"time":98000,"text":"for the first time."},{"time":100000,"text":"And it was so beautiful that I've been back there"},{"time":103000,"text":"ever since, for the last seven years."},{"time":105000,"text":"I love the place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107000,"text":"But I have seen that place change"},{"time":110000,"text":"beyond all description,"},{"time":112000,"text":"just in that short period of time."},{"time":114000,"text":"I have seen polar bears walking across very, very thin ice"},{"time":117000,"text":"in search of food."},{"time":119000,"text":"I have swum in front of glaciers"},{"time":122000,"text":"which have retreated so much."},{"time":124000,"text":"And I have also, every year,"},{"time":126000,"text":"seen less and less sea ice."},{"time":129000,"text":"And I wanted the world to know what was happening up there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132000,"text":"In the two years before my swim,"},{"time":135000,"text":"23 percent of the arctic sea ice cover"},{"time":138000,"text":"just melted away."},{"time":140000,"text":"And I wanted to really shake the lapels of world leaders"},{"time":143000,"text":"to get them to understand what is happening."},{"time":147000,"text":"So I decided to do this symbolic swim"},{"time":149000,"text":"at the top of the world, in a place which should be frozen over,"},{"time":153000,"text":"but which now is rapidly unfreezing."},{"time":156000,"text":"And the message was very clear:"},{"time":158000,"text":"Climate change is for real,"},{"time":160000,"text":"and we need to do something about it."},{"time":162000,"text":"And we need to do something about it right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166000,"text":"Well, swimming across the North Pole,"},{"time":169000,"text":"it's not an ordinary thing to do."},{"time":172000,"text":"I mean, just to put it in perspective,"},{"time":174000,"text":"27 degrees is the temperature of a normal indoor swimming pool."},{"time":178000,"text":"This morning, the temperature of the English Channel was 18 degrees."},{"time":183000,"text":"The passengers who fell off the Titanic"},{"time":186000,"text":"fell into water of just five degrees centigrade."},{"time":189000,"text":"Fresh water freezes at zero."},{"time":192000,"text":"And the water at the North Pole is minus 1.7."},{"time":196000,"text":"It's fucking freezing."},{"time":198000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":200000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":203000,"text":"I'm sorry, but there is no other way to describe it."},{"time":206000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"And so I had to assemble an incredible team around me"},{"time":214000,"text":"to help me with this task."},{"time":216000,"text":"I assembled this team of 29 people from 10 nations."},{"time":223000,"text":"Some people think that swimming is a very solo sport,"},{"time":226000,"text":"you just dive into the sea and off you go."},{"time":228000,"text":"It couldn't be further from the truth for me."},{"time":231000,"text":"And I then went and did a huge amount of training,"},{"time":234000,"text":"swimming in icy water, backwards and forwards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237000,"text":"But the most important thing was to train my mind"},{"time":240000,"text":"to prepare myself for what was going to happen."},{"time":242000,"text":"And I had to visualize the swim."},{"time":244000,"text":"I had to see it from the beginning all the way to the end."},{"time":247000,"text":"I had to taste the salt water in my mouth."},{"time":249000,"text":"I had to see my coach screaming for me,"},{"time":251000,"text":"\"Come on Lewis! Come on! Go! Go! Go! Don't slow down!\""},{"time":255000,"text":"And so I literally swam across the North Pole"},{"time":258000,"text":"hundreds and hundreds of times in my mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262000,"text":"And then, after a year of training, I felt ready."},{"time":265000,"text":"I felt confident that I could actually"},{"time":267000,"text":"do this swim."},{"time":269000,"text":"So myself and the five members of the team,"},{"time":271000,"text":"we hitched a ride on an icebreaker"},{"time":273000,"text":"which was going to the North Pole."},{"time":275000,"text":"And on day four, we decided to just do a quick"},{"time":278000,"text":"five minute test swim."},{"time":280000,"text":"I had never swum in water of minus 1.7 degrees before,"},{"time":284000,"text":"because it's just impossible to train"},{"time":286000,"text":"in those types of conditions."},{"time":288000,"text":"So we stopped the ship, as you do."},{"time":290000,"text":"We all got down onto the ice,"},{"time":292000,"text":"and I then got into my swimming costume"},{"time":294000,"text":"and I dived into the sea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297000,"text":"I have never in my life felt anything"},{"time":300000,"text":"like that moment."},{"time":302000,"text":"I could barely breathe. I was gasping for air."},{"time":304000,"text":"I was hyperventilating so much,"},{"time":307000,"text":"and within seconds my hands were numb."},{"time":309000,"text":"And it was -- the paradox is"},{"time":311000,"text":"that you're in freezing cold water,"},{"time":313000,"text":"but actually you're on fire."},{"time":315000,"text":"I swam as hard as I could for five minutes."},{"time":317000,"text":"I remember just trying to get out of the water."},{"time":319000,"text":"I climbed out of the ice."},{"time":321000,"text":"And I remember taking the goggles off my face"},{"time":324000,"text":"and looking down at my hands in sheer shock,"},{"time":327000,"text":"because my fingers"},{"time":330000,"text":"had swollen so much that they were like sausages."},{"time":333000,"text":"And they were swollen so much, I couldn't even close them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338000,"text":"What had happened is that we are made partially of water,"},{"time":341000,"text":"and when water freezes it expands."},{"time":344000,"text":"And so what had actually happened is"},{"time":346000,"text":"that the cells in my fingers had frozen and expanded."},{"time":350000,"text":"And they had burst. And I was in so much agony."},{"time":354000,"text":"I immediately got rushed onto the ship and into a hot shower."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357000,"text":"And I remember standing underneath the hot shower"},{"time":360000,"text":"and trying to defrost my fingers."},{"time":364000,"text":"And I thought, in two days' time, I was going to do this swim across the North Pole."},{"time":370000,"text":"I was going to try and do a 20-minute swim,"},{"time":374000,"text":"for one kilometer across the North Pole."},{"time":376000,"text":"And this dream which I had had ever since I was a young boy"},{"time":379000,"text":"with my father, was just going out the window."},{"time":382000,"text":"There is no possibility that this was going to happen."},{"time":387000,"text":"And I remember then getting out of the shower"},{"time":389000,"text":"and realizing I couldn't even feel my hands."},{"time":393000,"text":"And for a swimmer, you need to feel your hands"},{"time":396000,"text":"because you need to be able to grab the water"},{"time":399000,"text":"and pull it through with you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401000,"text":"The next morning, I woke up"},{"time":403000,"text":"and I was in such a state of depression,"},{"time":407000,"text":"and all I could think about was Sir Ranulph Fiennes."},{"time":410000,"text":"For those of you who don't know him, he's the great British explorer."},{"time":413000,"text":"A number of years ago, he tried to ski all the way to the North Pole."},{"time":418000,"text":"He accidentally fell through the ice into the sea."},{"time":421000,"text":"And after just three minutes in that water,"},{"time":424000,"text":"he was able"},{"time":426000,"text":"to get himself out."},{"time":428000,"text":"And his hands were so badly frostbitten"},{"time":430000,"text":"that he had to return to England."},{"time":432000,"text":"He went to a local hospital and there they said,"},{"time":435000,"text":"\"Ran, there is no possibility"},{"time":438000,"text":"of us being able to save these fingers."},{"time":440000,"text":"We are going to actually have to take them off.\""},{"time":443000,"text":"And Ran decided to go into his tool shed"},{"time":448000,"text":"and take out a saw"},{"time":450000,"text":"and do it himself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454000,"text":"And all I could think of was, if that happened to Ran after three minutes,"},{"time":458000,"text":"and I can't feel my hands after five minutes,"},{"time":461000,"text":"what on earth is going to happen if I try 20 minutes?"},{"time":465000,"text":"At the very best, I'm going to end up losing some fingers."},{"time":468000,"text":"And at worst, I didn't even want to think about it."},{"time":473000,"text":"We carried on sailing through the ice packs towards the North Pole."}]},{"cues":[{"time":476000,"text":"And my close friend David, he saw the way I was thinking,"},{"time":479000,"text":"and he came up to me and he said, \"Lewis,"},{"time":481000,"text":"I've known you since you were 18 years old."},{"time":486000,"text":"I've known you, and I know, Lewis,"},{"time":489000,"text":"deep down, right deep down here,"},{"time":491000,"text":"that you are going to make this swim."},{"time":493000,"text":"I so believe in you Lewis. I've seen the way you've been training."},{"time":496000,"text":"And I realize the reason why you're going to do this."},{"time":499000,"text":"This is such an important swim."},{"time":502000,"text":"We stand at a very, very important moment in this history,"},{"time":506000,"text":"and you're going to make a symbolic swim here"},{"time":509000,"text":"to try to shake the lapels of world leaders."},{"time":511000,"text":"Lewis, have the courage to go in there,"},{"time":513000,"text":"because we are going to look after you every moment of it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":518000,"text":"And I just, I got so much confidence from him saying that,"},{"time":521000,"text":"because he knew me so well."},{"time":524000,"text":"So we carried on sailing and we arrived at the North Pole."},{"time":527000,"text":"And we stopped the ship,"},{"time":529000,"text":"and it was just as the scientists had predicted."},{"time":531000,"text":"There were open patches of sea everywhere."},{"time":534000,"text":"And I went down into my cabin"},{"time":536000,"text":"and I put on my swimming costume."},{"time":538000,"text":"And then the doctor strapped on a chest monitor,"},{"time":540000,"text":"which measures my core body temperature"},{"time":542000,"text":"and my heart rate."},{"time":544000,"text":"And then we walked out onto the ice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547000,"text":"And I remember looking into the ice,"},{"time":551000,"text":"and there were big chunks of white ice in there,"},{"time":553000,"text":"and the water was completely black."},{"time":557000,"text":"I had never seen black water before."},{"time":559000,"text":"And it is 4,200 meters deep."},{"time":563000,"text":"And I said to myself, \"Lewis, don't look left, don't look right."},{"time":566000,"text":"Just scuttle forward and go for it.\""},{"time":570000,"text":"And so I now want to show you a short video"},{"time":572000,"text":"of what happened there on the ice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":591000,"text":"Narrator (Video): We're just sailing out of harbor now, and it's at this stage"},{"time":594000,"text":"when one can have a bit of a wobble mentally."},{"time":597000,"text":"Everything just looks so gray around here,"},{"time":601000,"text":"and looks so cold."},{"time":638000,"text":"We've just seen our first polar bears."},{"time":640000,"text":"It was absolutely magical."},{"time":642000,"text":"A mother and a cub, such a beautiful sight."},{"time":644000,"text":"And to think that in 30, 40 years"},{"time":646000,"text":"they could become extinct."},{"time":648000,"text":"It's a very frightening, very, very frightening thought."},{"time":677000,"text":"We're finally at the North Pole. This is"},{"time":679000,"text":"months and months and months of dreaming to get here,"},{"time":682000,"text":"years of training and planning and preparation."},{"time":686000,"text":"Ooh. In a couple of hours' time I'm going to get in here and do my swim."},{"time":689000,"text":"It's all a little bit frightening,"},{"time":691000,"text":"and emotional."},{"time":733000,"text":"Amundson, you ready? Amudson: Ready."},{"time":745000,"text":"Lewis Pugh: Ten seconds to swim. Ten seconds to swim."},{"time":893000,"text":"Take the goggles off. Take the goggles off!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":912000,"text":"Man: Take the shoes. Take the shoes."},{"time":915000,"text":"Well done lad! You did it! You did it Lewis!"},{"time":918000,"text":"You did it! You did it man!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":943000,"text":"LP: How on earth did we do that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":945000,"text":"Man: Against the current! You did it against the current!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":950000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":965000,"text":"LP: Thank you very much. Thank you very much."},{"time":968000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":974000,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":976000,"text":"Audience: Encore!"},{"time":978000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":980000,"text":"LP: I'd just like to end off by just saying this:"},{"time":982000,"text":"It took me four months again to feel my hands."},{"time":985000,"text":"But was it worth it? Yes, absolutely it was."},{"time":987000,"text":"There are very, very few people who don't know now"},{"time":990000,"text":"about what is happening in the Arctic."},{"time":992000,"text":"And people ask me, \"Lewis, what can we do about climate change?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":995000,"text":"And I say to them,"},{"time":997000,"text":"I think we need to do three things."},{"time":999000,"text":"The first thing we need to do is we need to break this problem down"},{"time":1002000,"text":"into manageable chunks."},{"time":1004000,"text":"You saw during that video all those flags."},{"time":1007000,"text":"Those flags represented the countries"},{"time":1010000,"text":"from which my team came from."},{"time":1012000,"text":"And equally, when it comes to climate change,"},{"time":1014000,"text":"every single country is going to have to make cuts."},{"time":1018000,"text":"Britain, America, Japan,"},{"time":1020000,"text":"South Africa, the Congo."},{"time":1022000,"text":"All of us together, we're all on the same ship together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1026000,"text":"The second thing we need to do is"},{"time":1028000,"text":"we need to just look back"},{"time":1030000,"text":"at how far we have come"},{"time":1032000,"text":"in such a short period of time."},{"time":1034000,"text":"I remember, just a few years ago, speaking about climate change,"},{"time":1037000,"text":"and people heckling me in the back"},{"time":1039000,"text":"and saying it doesn't even exist."},{"time":1042000,"text":"I've just come back from giving a series of speeches"},{"time":1045000,"text":"in some of the poorest townships in South Africa"},{"time":1048000,"text":"to young children as young as 10 years old."},{"time":1051000,"text":"Four or five children sitting behind a desk,"},{"time":1054000,"text":"and even in those poorest conditions,"},{"time":1057000,"text":"they all have a very, very good grasp"},{"time":1060000,"text":"of climate change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1062000,"text":"We need to believe in ourselves."},{"time":1064000,"text":"Now is the time to believe."},{"time":1066000,"text":"We've come a long way. We're doing good."},{"time":1069000,"text":"But the most important thing we must do"},{"time":1071000,"text":"is, I think, we must all walk to the end of our lives"},{"time":1075000,"text":"and turn around, and ask ourselves a most fundamental question."},{"time":1080000,"text":"And that is, \"What type of world do we want to live in,"},{"time":1085000,"text":"and what decision are we going to make today"},{"time":1088000,"text":"to ensure that we all live"},{"time":1090000,"text":"in a sustainable world?\""},{"time":1093000,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen, thank you very, very much."},{"time":1095000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}